snippet.title: Roblox Family Goldie Get Well Routine - Bloxburg RP
snippet.description:
Join us in today's heartwarming video as Roblox Goldie takes a sick day and stays home with a nasty stomach bug and sadly misses out on her school's exciting field day. Titi tries to take her of her at home and makes her food but Goldie needs to see a doctor. Lets see what happens next in this Bloxburg family roleplay.
